
==INSTALLATION==
    
cd nginx-1.0.2
patch -p1 < /path/to/this/directory/upstream_keepalive_1.0.2.patch

#add the module
./configure --add-module=/path/to/this/directory


==EXAMPLE==

upstream backends {
    server 10.0.0.1;
    server 10.0.0.2;

    keepalive 128;
}

The ngx_http_upstream_keepalive_module's document is here:
https://github.com/yaoweibin/nginx_upstream_keepalive_patch/raw/master/ngx_http_upstream_keepalive/README

